{"tid":2004721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"痴左 台灣旺旺蔡衍明 總經理 示範直接飲 洗潔劑 次氯酸水","createTime":"2020-05-06T15:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:27:49.000Z","uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea12058d16a6334a53d230c23465a71f7dc35161","tid":2004721,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"「旺旺」集團所出產的次氯酸水產品「水神」，因包裝幾乎與礦泉水雷同，造成民眾誤飲。民進黨立委吳玉琴、綠黨新竹縣議員余筱菁今（29日）舉行記者會，提醒民眾並要求標識清楚勿食用字樣。不料「旺旺」代表卻到場踢館，甚至當場拿出自己帶來的「水神」，喝下肚證明「食用無害」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民進黨立委林淑芬稍早也在臉書表示，衛福部說次氯酸水不能喝，業者派員工在現場直接喝給你看，還強調「誤食無害」，她呼籲「衛福部要不要管一管」！<br />\n<br />\n林淑芬另一篇貼文，還貼出旺旺集團董事長蔡衍明，日前在記者會上示範喝「水神」的畫面，林淑芬強調，「TFDA都說次氯酸水不能直接噴在人身上了，還示範喝下去，還叫大家直接噴眼睛噴鼻子。」文末驚呼，「我的天啊！」<br />\n<br />\n林淑芬貼文，引起網友熱議，「瘋了！他知道次氯酸水的原物料是什麼嗎？」、「這種行為沒有違反食品或藥品的相關法條嗎?」、「好像是夜市賣藥的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-29/399140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-29%2F399140&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=b1c5da8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-29/399140</a>"},{"pid":"acb23097bec9d9aef8d0c561715039e1910cbe41","tid":2004721,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zlHLAYVblRs?t=369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzlHLAYVblRs%3Ft%3D369&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=9179985e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zlHLAYVblRs?t=369</a>"},{"pid":"2bd0cd603394ff1e2f819f5dd84fa379ce19e477","tid":2004721,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UnmQYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UnmQYL.jpg&h=46fbddde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ncmnAqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FncmnAqr.jpg&h=6d4b25dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mohw.gov.tw/cp-4343-51863-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mohw.gov.tw%2Fcp-4343-51863-1.html&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=6892ca0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mohw.gov.tw/cp-4343-51863-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n正確使用次氯酸水<br />\n資料來源：食品藥物管理署建檔日期：109-03-07更新時間：109-03-09<br />\n次氯酸在我國可作為「食品用洗潔劑」，用於食品、食品器具、容器及包裝之消毒用途，並非我國准用之食品添加物，亦不可以飲用。"}]}